title: Nightmare Beach (1989 Horror) 500,000 students and a killer to stop

sources.title: Nightmare Beach (1989 Horror) 500,000 students and a killer to stop
sources.description:
The beach of terror: After the execution of a motorcycle gang leader convicted of murder, a helmeted biker goes on a killing spree during spring break in Florida.


Original title: Nightmare Beach (1989) AKA: Welcome to Spring Break


Watch the uncensored (Members Only) version: https://youtu.be/58JFqAZgWjM


Directors: James Justice, Umberto Lenzi
Writers: Umberto Lenzi, Vittorio Rambaldi, James Justice
Stars: Nicolas De Toth, Sarah Buxton, Rawley Valverde
Genre: Horror


@CultCinemaClassics
